- **Deprecated / old:** `https://bran-be-production.up.railway.app` (do not use)

## Slack Event Subscriptions

- Request URL: `https://bran-be-production-3549.up.railway.app/api/slack/events`
- Slash command URL: `https://bran-be-production-3549.up.railway.app/api/slack/commands`
- Cron check: `https://bran-be-production-3549.up.railway.app/api/cron/eta-check`

## Deploy verification

A healthy attendance deploy returns `"build":"attendance-v1"` from `GET /` and echoes Slack `url_verification` challenges from `POST /api/slack/events`.

## Attendance access

JWT attendance APIs (`/api/eta/*`, `/:lang/v1/attendance/*`) are restricted to roles `admin` and `chief_of_staff`. Frontend should hide the Attendance nav/page for every other role.
